# Cloudflare Pages/Workers static asset headers.
# "no-cache" does NOT mean "don't cache" — browsers may store the file but
# MUST revalidate with the server (ETag/304) before using it. This keeps
# the site fast while guaranteeing that every deploy takes effect
# immediately, instead of browsers running stale cached JS/CSS for days.
/*
  Cache-Control: no-cache
  X-Content-Type-Options: nosniff
  Referrer-Policy: strict-origin-when-cross-origin
